<td style="width: 46.02%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: inset black 1.0pt; border-right: inset black 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: inset black .75pt; mso-border-left-alt: inset black .75pt; mso-border-alt: inset black .75pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt; height: 45.9pt;" width="46%">
<p>a handful of {sapphire} (type of seaweed)</p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 2; height: 60.6pt;">
<td style="width: 14.66%; border: inset black 1.0pt; border-top: none; mso-border-top-alt: inset black .75pt; mso-border-alt: inset black .75pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt; height: 60.6pt;" width="14%">
<p><strong>Organic shop</strong></p>
</td>
<td style="width: 39.28%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: inset black 1.0pt; border-right: inset black 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: inset black .75pt; mso-border-left-alt: inset black .75pt; mso-border-alt: inset black .75pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt; height: 60.6pt;" width="39%">
<p>beans and a {melon} for dessert</p>
</td>
<td style="width: 46.02%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: inset black 1.0pt; border-right: inset black 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: inset black .75pt; mso-border-left-alt: inset black .75pt; mso-border-alt: inset black .75pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt; height: 60.6pt;" width="46%">
<p>spices and {coconut}</p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 3; mso-yfti-lastrow: yes; height: 45.9pt;">
<td style="width: 14.66%; border: inset black 1.0pt; border-top: none; mso-border-top-alt: inset black .75pt; mso-border-alt: inset black .75pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt; height: 45.9pt;" width="14%">
<p><strong>Bakery</strong></p>
</td>
<td style="width: 39.28%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: inset black 1.0pt; border-right: inset black 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: inset black .75pt; mso-border-left-alt: inset black .75pt; mso-border-alt: inset black .75pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt; height: 45.9pt;" width="39%">
<p>a brown loaf</p>
</td>
