<h3 data-section-id="ggceya" data-start="502" data-end="516"> </h3>', NULL, 'summary_completion', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', '[{"content": "<p>1</p>"}]', 1);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('6ff90277-f7b1-4e49-bc63-cbd146d90535', 'a2a298b7-d8c1-4d89-bbcd-872dc7bb5b9c', 'checkbox', 'Questions 23 and 24', '', '<p>In his assignment, which <strong>TWO </strong>aspects of outdoor play does Ravi want to focus on?</p>
<p>Choose <strong>TWO </strong>letters, A-E.</p>', 'multiple_choice', 'null', '[{"correct": true, "option_text": "A. How it helps children to evaluate risk"}, {"correct": false, "option_text": "B. How it broadens their horizons"}, {"correct": false, "option_text": "C. How it aids children’s muscular development"}, {"correct": true, "option_text": "D. How it improves children’s digestion"}, {"correct": false, "option_text": "E. How it teaches children about the environment"}]', 'null', 'null', 'null', 1);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('86e0c6f8-8640-4c40-9c4e-cb61cc5b6f5c', 'c09ee800-0d6b-47ee-bfa4-c4e3bd5263b3', 'fillup', 'Questions 19–22', '<p id="p-rc_5d06c53be89a37be-219" data-path-to-node="7"><span class="citation-24836 citation-24837 citation-24838 citation-24839 citation-24840 citation-end-24840">Complete the sentences below.<sup class="superscript" data-turn-source-index="17"><!----></sup></span><span class="citation-24836 citation-24837 citation-24838 citation-24839 citation-end-24839"><sup class="superscript" data-turn-source-index="18"><!----></sup></span><span class="citation-24836 citation-24837 citation-24838 citation-end-24838"><sup class="superscript" data-turn-source-index="19"><!----></sup></span><span class="citation-24836 citation-24837 citation-end-24837"><sup class="superscript" data-turn-source-index="20"><!----></sup></span><span class="citation-24836 citation-end-24836"><sup class="superscript" data-turn-source-index="21"><!----></sup></span></p>
<p data-path-to-node="7"><span class="citation-24831 citation-24832 citation-24833 citation-24834 citation-24835">Choose </span><strong data-path-to-node="7" data-index-in-node="37"><span class="citation-24831 citation-24832 citation-24833 citation-24834 citation-24835">ONE WORD ONLY</span></strong><span class="citation-24831 citation-24832 citation-24833 citation-24834 citation-24835 citation-end-24835"> from the passage for each answer.<sup class="superscript" data-turn-source-index="22"><!----></sup></span><span class="citation-24831 citation-24832 citation-24833 citation-24834 citation-end-24834"><sup class="superscript" data-turn-source-index="23"><!----></sup></span><span class="citation-24831 citation-24832 citation-24833 citation-end-24833"><sup class="superscript" data-turn-source-index="24"><!----></sup></span><span class="citation-24831 citation-24832 citation-end-24832"><sup class="superscript" data-turn-source-index="25"><!----></sup></span><span class="citation-24831 citation-end-24831"><sup class="superscript" data-turn-source-index="26"><!----></sup></span></p>
<p data-path-to-node="7"><span class="citation-24826 citation-24827 citation-24828 citation-24829 citation-24830 citation-end-24830">Write your answers in boxes 19–22 </span><span class="citation-24826 citation-24827 citation-24828 citation-24829 citation-end-24829">on your answer sheet.</span></p>
<div class="source-inline-chip-container ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----></div>
<p><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></p>
<ul>
<li id="p-rc_5d06c53be89a37be-220" data-path-to-node="8">
<p><span class="citation-24822 citation-24823 citation-24824 citation-24825 citation-end-24825">Performance stress involves many demands on the athlete, for example, coping with the possible risk of {injury}.</span></p>
</li>
<li data-path-to-node="8">
<p><span class="citation-24818 citation-24819 citation-24820 citation-end-24820">Cortisol can cause tennis players to produce fewer good {serves} .<sup class="superscript" data-turn-source-index="37"><!----></sup></span><span class="citation-24818 citation-24819 citation-end-24819"><sup class="superscript" data-turn-source-index="38"><!----></sup></span><span class="citation-24818 citation-end-24818"><sup class="superscript" data-turn-source-index="39"><!----></sup></span></p>
</li>
<li data-path-to-node="8">
<p><span class="citation-24815 citation-24816 citation-24817 citation-end-24817">Psychologists can help athletes to view their physiological responses as the effect of a positive <sup class="superscript" data-turn-source-index="40"><!----></sup></span><span class="citation-24815 citation-24816 citation-end-24816">feeling such as {excitement} .<sup class="superscript" data-turn-source-index="41"><!----></sup></span><span class="citation-24815 citation-end-24815"><sup class="superscript" data-turn-source-index="42"><!----></sup></span></p>
</li>
<li data-path-to-node="8">
<p><span class="citation-24813 citation-24814 citation-end-24814">{Visualisation|Visualization} is an example of a psychological technique which can reduce an athlete''s stress respons<sup class="superscript" data-turn-source-index="43"><!----></sup></span><span class="citation-24813 citation-end-24813">es.<sup class="superscript" data-turn-source-index="44"><!----></sup></span></p>
</li>
</ul>', NULL, 'summary_completion', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', '[{"content": "<p data-path-to-node=\"4\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"4\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">19. injury — {for example, coping with the possible risk of injury}</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"5\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"5,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"5,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng (Đoạn B):</strong> <em data-path-to-node=\"5,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"20\">\"...the athlete''s concerns about the difficulty of the event... and any potential dangers such as <strong data-path-to-node=\"5,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"118\">injury</strong>.\"</em></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"5,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"5,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> \"Potential dangers\" (mối nguy hiểm tiềm tàng) tương ứng với cụm \"possible risk\" (rủi ro có thể xảy ra). Một ví dụ cụ thể về rủi ro này được bài đọc nêu ra chính là chấn thương (<strong data-path-to-node=\"5,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"189\">injury</strong>).</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"6\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"6\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">20. serves — {Cortisol can cause tennis players to produce fewer good serves}</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"7\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"7,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"7,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng (Đoạn D):</strong> <em data-path-to-node=\"7,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"20\">\"In tennis players, <strong data-path-to-node=\"7,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"40\">cortisol</strong> has been associated with more <strong data-path-to-node=\"7,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"79\">unsuccessful serves</strong>...\"</em></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"7,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"7,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> \"Associated with more unsuccessful serves\" (liên quan đến việc có nhiều cú giao bóng hỏng hơn) đồng nghĩa với việc tạo ra ít cú giao bóng tốt hơn (<strong data-path-to-node=\"7,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"159\">fewer good serves</strong>). Danh từ cần điền là những cú giao bóng (<strong data-path-to-node=\"7,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"219\">serves</strong>).</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"8\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"8\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">21. excitement — {help athletes to view their physiological responses as... excitement}</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"9\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"9,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng (Đoạn F):</strong> <em data-path-to-node=\"9,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"20\">\"...helping them see a <strong data-path-to-node=\"9,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"43\">higher heart rate as excitement</strong>, rather than nerves.\"</em></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"9,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> \"View their physiological responses\" (ví dụ như nhịp tim tăng) như một cảm giác tích cực là sự phấn khích (<strong data-path-to-node=\"9,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"119\">excitement</strong>) thay vì lo lắng.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"10\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"10\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">22. Visualisation (hoặc Visualization) — {Visualisation is an example of a psychological technique}</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"11\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"11,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"11,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng (Đoạn F):</strong> <em data-path-to-node=\"11,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"20\">\"Developing psychological skills, such as <strong data-path-to-node=\"11,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"62\">visualisation</strong>, can also help decrease physiological responses to threat.\"</em></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"11,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"11,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Kỹ năng/kỹ thuật tâm lý (<strong data-path-to-node=\"11,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"37\">psychological technique</strong>) được bài đọc đưa ra làm ví dụ để giảm phản ứng stress chính là hình dung (<strong data-path-to-node=\"11,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"136\">visualisation</strong>).</p>\n</li>\n</ul>"}]', 1);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('b195fb51-9ac6-411e-a509-33b0110aded5', '731bdf95-ba82-4d9b-9c69-947c45d2315f', 'fillup', 'Questions 31–40', '<p data-path-to-node="3">Complete the notes below.</p>
<p data-path-to-node="4">Write <strong data-path-to-node="4" data-index-in-node="6">ONE WORD ONLY</strong> for each answer.</p>
<table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 99.9592%; height: 2px; border-spacing: 2px; border: 1px solid #000000;" border="1"><colgroup><col style="width: 99.8776%;"></colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td style="padding: 2px; border-color: #000000;">
<p style="text-align: left;" data-path-to-node="5,0"><span style="font-size: 14pt;"><strong data-path-to-node="5,0" data-index-in-node="0">Microplastics</strong></span></p>
<p data-path-to-node="5,1"><strong data-path-to-node="5,1" data-index-in-node="0">Where microplastics come from</strong></p>
<ul data-path-to-node="5,2">
<li>
<p>fibres from some {clothing} during washing</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>the breakdown of large pieces of plastic</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>waste from industry</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>the action of vehicle tyres on roads</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p><strong data-path-to-node="5,3" data-index-in-node="0">Effects of microplastics</strong></p>
<ul data-path-to-node="5,4">
<li>
<p><span class="citation-69588 citation-69589">They cause injuries to the {mouths}</span><span class="citation-69588 citation-69589 citation-end-69589"> of wildlife and affect their digestive systems.<sup class="superscript" data-turn-source-index="1"><!----></sup></span><span class="citation-69588 citation-end-69588"><sup class="superscript" data-turn-source-index="2"><!----></sup></span><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></p>
</li>
<li>
<p><span class="citation-69586 citation-69587">They enter the food chain, e.g., in bottled and tap water, {salt}</span><span class="citation-69586 citation-69587 citation-end-69587"> and seafood.<sup class="superscript" data-turn-source-index="3"><!----></sup></span><span class="citation-69586 citation-end-69586"><sup class="superscript" data-turn-source-index="4"><!----></sup></span><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></p>
</li>
<li>
<p><span class="citation-69584 citation-69585 citation-end-69585">They may not affect human health, but they are already banned in skin cleaning products and {toothpaste}</span><span class="citation-69584 citation-end-69584"> in some countries.<sup class="superscript" data-turn-source-index="6"><!----></sup></span><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></p>
</li>
<li>
<p><span class="citation-69583 citation-end-69583">Microplastics enter the soil through the air, rain and {fertilisers|fertilizers}</span> .<!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p><strong data-path-to-node="5,5" data-index-in-node="0">Microplastics in the soil – a study by Anglia Ruskin University</strong></p>
<ul data-path-to-node="5,6">
<li>
<p>Earthworms are important because they add {nutrients} to the soil.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>The study aimed to find whether microplastics in earthworms affect the {growth} of plants.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>The study found that microplastics caused:</p>
<ul data-path-to-node="5,6,2,1">
<li>
<p>{weight} loss in earthworms</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>fewer seeds to germinate</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>a rise in the level of {acid} in the soil.</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<p>The study concluded:</p>
<ul data-path-to-node="5,6,3,1">
<li>
<p>soil should be seen as an important natural process.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>changes to soil damage both ecosystems and {society}</p>
</li>
</ul>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p> </p>', NULL, 'summary_completion', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', '[{"content": "<p>1</p>"}]', 0);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('19ec518d-1814-4bb0-8ccc-8eeaa8d015e4', 'e91fa672-f757-4df6-b10f-58605adc1d09', 'matrix', 'Questions 17–20', '', '<p data-start="95" data-end="181"><strong data-start="95" data-end="119">Label the map below.</strong><br data-start="119" data-end="122">Write the correct letter, <strong data-start="148" data-end="155">A–G</strong>, next to Questions 17–20.</p>
<h3 data-start="183" data-end="217"><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," width="435" height="384" loading="lazy"></h3>', 'choose_a_title', 'null', 'null', 'null', '{"layoutType": "simple", "matrixItems": [{"itemText": "bridge foundations", "correctCategoryLetter": "B"}, {"itemText": "rubbish pit", "correctCategoryLetter": "A"}, {"itemText": "meeting hall", "correctCategoryLetter": "G"}, {"itemText": "fish pond", "correctCategoryLetter": "E"}], "matrixCategories": [{"categoryText": "A", "categoryLetter": "A"}, {"categoryText": "B", "categoryLetter": "B"}, {"categoryText": "C", "categoryLetter": "C"}, {"categoryText": "D", "categoryLetter": "D"}, {"categoryText": "E", "categoryLetter": "E"}, {"categoryText": "F", "categoryLetter": "F"}, {"categoryText": "G", "categoryLetter": "G"}]}', 'null', 1);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('8757c1ae-fd47-4031-8e06-075aefcbc955', 'a2a298b7-d8c1-4d89-bbcd-872dc7bb5b9c', 'checkbox', 'Questions 25 and 26', '', '<p>According to Ravi, in which <strong>TWO </strong>ways are children’s periods of outdoor play now different from a generation ago?</p>
<p>Choose <strong>TWO</strong> letters, <strong>A-E.</strong></p>', 'multiple_choice', 'null', '[{"correct": false, "option_text": "A. They are less dangerous."}, {"correct": false, "option_text": "B. They involve fewer children."}, {"correct": true, "option_text": "C. They usually last a shorter time."}, {"correct": true, "option_text": "D. They include fewer made-up games."}, {"correct": false, "option_text": "E. They involve fewer chasing games."}]', 'null', 'null', 'null', 2);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('087cc2b2-4816-4289-a661-baddbadb2ef7', 'd31276a3-8a0c-4b27-9e55-e0da2be3c559', 'radio', 'Questions 1–6', '', '<p>Choose <strong data-path-to-node="3" data-index-in-node="7">TRUE</strong> if the statement agrees with the information given in the text, choose <strong data-path-to-node="3" data-index-in-node="83">FALSE</strong> if the statement contradicts the information, or choose <strong data-path-to-node="3" data-index-in-node="145">NOT GIVEN</strong> if there is no information on this.</p>', 'true_false_not_given', '[{"correct": 1, "options": [{"option_text": "TRUE"}, {"option_text": "FALSE"}, {"option_text": "NOT GIVEN"}], "question": "In 1986 Luc Long had been looking for an opportunity to dive in the Rhône for some time."}, {"correct": 2, "options": [{"option_text": "TRUE"}, {"option_text": "FALSE"}, {"option_text": "NOT GIVEN"}], "question": "Long and his friend were the first divers to find Roman remains in the Rhône."}, {"correct": 1, "options": [{"option_text": "TRUE"}, {"option_text": "FALSE"}, {"option_text": "NOT GIVEN"}], "question": "Long’s work in the Rhône attracted immediate interest."}, {"correct": 0, "options": [{"option_text": "TRUE"}, {"option_text": "FALSE"}, {"option_text": "NOT GIVEN"}], "question": "It was thought that the Neptune statue would be of interest to thieves."}, {"correct": 0, "options": [{"option_text": "TRUE"}, {"option_text": "FALSE"}, {"option_text": "NOT GIVEN"}], "question": "Benoît Poinard doubted that the barge could be raised in one diving season."}, {"correct": 2, "options": [{"option_text": "TRUE"}, {"option_text": "FALSE"}, {"option_text": "NOT GIVEN"}], "question": "The restorers were surprised to discover a silver coin on the barge."}]', 'null', 'null', 'null', '[{"content": "<p data-path-to-node=\"4\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"4\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">1. In 1986 Luc Long had been looking for an opportunity to dive in the Rhône for some time. — {FALSE}</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"5\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"5,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"5,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng (Đoạn 2):</strong> <em data-path-to-node=\"5,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"20\">“In 1986, a friend persuaded him to dive for the first time in his home river. <strong data-path-to-node=\"5,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"99\">Long reluctantly agreed</strong>.”</em></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"5,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"5,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Câu hỏi nói Long đã tìm kiếm cơ hội lặn ở sông Rhône từ lâu. Tuy nhiên, bài đọc cho biết ông chỉ lặn vì được bạn thuyết phục và ông đã <strong data-path-to-node=\"5,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"147\">“reluctantly agreed”</strong> (đồng ý một cách miễn cưỡng). Hai thông tin này trái ngược nhau hoàn toàn.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"6\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"6\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">2. Long and his friend were the first divers to find Roman remains in the Rhône. — {NOT GIVEN}</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"7\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"7,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"7,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng (Đoạn 2):</strong> <em data-path-to-node=\"7,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"20\">“The two men… discovered an ancient Roman jar – known as an amphora…”</em></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"7,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"7,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Bài đọc chỉ kể về việc Long và bạn của ông tìm thấy cổ vật, nhưng <strong data-path-to-node=\"7,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"78\">không hề khẳng định</strong> họ là những người đầu tiên tìm thấy tàn tích La Mã ở con sông này hay đã có ai tìm thấy trước đó chưa. Vì thiếu thông tin để so sánh “người đầu tiên”, đáp án là Not Given.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"8\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"8\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">3. Long’s work in the Rhône attracted immediate interest. — {FALSE}</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"9\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"9,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng (Đoạn 3):</strong> <em data-path-to-node=\"9,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"20\">“For the <strong data-path-to-node=\"9,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"29\">first 20 years or so, no one paid much attention</strong> to what Long was doing.”</em></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"9,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Câu hỏi nói công việc của Long thu hút sự chú ý ngay lập tức (<em data-path-to-node=\"9,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"74\">immediate interest</em>). Thực tế bài đọc ghi rõ trong khoảng 20 năm đầu không ai quan tâm đến việc ông làm. Thông tin này trái ngược nhau.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"10\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"10\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">4. It was thought that the Neptune statue would be of interest to thieves. — {TRUE}</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"11\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"11,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"11,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng (Đoạn 3):</strong> <em data-path-to-node=\"11,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"20\">“The French customs police warned Long that <strong data-path-to-node=\"11,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"64\">antiquities thieves might be watching</strong> his operation. So when his divers found a two-metre statue of the god Neptune, <strong data-path-to-node=\"11,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"181\">they brought it to the surface at night</strong>.”</em></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"11,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"11,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Cảnh sát đã cảnh báo về kẻ trộm, và vì lo ngại bức tượng Neptune bị đánh cắp nên họ đã phải đưa nó lên mặt nước vào ban đêm. Điều này xác nhận rằng bức tượng được cho là sẽ thu hút sự quan tâm của kẻ trộm.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"12\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"12\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">5. Benoît Poinard doubted that the barge could be raised in one diving season. — {TRUE}</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"13\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"13,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"13,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng (Đoạn 5):</strong> <em data-path-to-node=\"13,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"20\">“‘<strong data-path-to-node=\"13,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"22\">We thought the project was doomed to fail</strong>,’ said Benoit Poinard… Three or four months would not be enough to excavate Arles-Rhône 3.”</em></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"13,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"13,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Poinard tin rằng dự án sẽ thất bại vì thời gian lặn an toàn trên sông Rhône quá ngắn (chỉ 3-4 tháng), không đủ để trục vớt con tàu trong một mùa. Tức là ông nghi ngờ khả năng thành công của việc trục vớt trong một mùa lặn.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"14\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"14\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">6. The restorers were surprised to discover a silver coin on the barge. — {NOT GIVEN}</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"15\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"15,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"15,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng (Đoạn 6):</strong> <em data-path-to-node=\"15,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"20\">“When the restorers were taking the boat apart, they also found a silver coin… <strong data-path-to-node=\"15,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"101\">it had been put there to bring good luck</strong>.”</em></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"15,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"15,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Bài đọc có nhắc đến việc tìm thấy đồng xu bạc và lý do nó ở đó (để cầu may), nhưng <strong data-path-to-node=\"15,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"95\">không có thông tin</strong> nào nói rằng các nhà phục chế cảm thấy “ngạc nhiên” (<em data-path-to-node=\"15,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"167\">surprised</em>). </p>\n</li>\n</ul>"}]', 0);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('0d4bd0cc-84c6-43e5-b1f8-227756a7427f', 'addc55a1-cd76-4b01-8c51-1ca14e40ccae', 'fillup', 'Questions 1–10', '<p data-start="121" data-end="200">Write <strong data-start="155" data-end="183">ONE WORD AND/OR A NUMBER</strong> for each answer.</p>
<div class="TyagGW_tableContainer">
<div class="group TyagGW_tableWrapper flex flex-col-reverse w-fit" tabindex="-1">
<table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 101.427%; height: 485.229px; border-spacing: 3px; border: 1px solid #000000;" border="1"><colgroup> <col style="width: 14.3662%;"> <col style="width: 28.7324%;"> <col style="width: 28.7324%;"> <col style="width: 28.169%;"></colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr style="height: 53.0556px;">
<td style="text-align: center; border-color: #000000;"><strong>Name of restaurant</strong></td>
<td style="text-align: center; border-color: #000000;"><strong>Location</strong></td>
<td style="text-align: center; border-color: #000000;"><strong>Reason for recommendation</strong></td>
<td style="text-align: center; border-color: #000000;"><strong>Other comments</strong></td>
</tr>
<tr style="height: 114.618px;">
<td style="border-color: #000000;">The Junction</td>
<td style="border-color: #000000;">Greyson Street, near the station</td>
<td style="border-color: #000000;">Good for people who are especially keen on <strong data-start="459" data-end="471">{fish}</strong></td>
<td style="border-color: #000000;">Quite expensiveThe <strong data-start="497" data-end="509">{roof}</strong> is a good place for a drink</td>
</tr>
<tr style="height: 167.778px;">
<td style="border-color: #000000;">Paloma</td>
<td style="border-color: #000000;">In Bow Street, next to the cinema</td>
<td style="border-color: #000000;"><strong data-start="591" data-end="603">{Spanish}</strong> food, good for sharing</td>
<td style="border-color: #000000;">Staff are very friendlyNeed to pay £50 depositA limited selection of <strong data-start="706" data-end="718">{vegetarian}</strong> food on the menu</td>
</tr>
<tr style="height: 149.778px;">
<td style="border-color: #000000;">The {Audley}</td>
<td style="border-color: #000000;">At the top of a <strong data-start="775" data-end="787">{hotel}</strong></td>
<td style="border-color: #000000;">A famous chefAll the <strong data-start="815" data-end="827">{reviews}</strong> are very goodOnly uses <strong data-start="855" data-end="867">{local}</strong> ingredients</td>
<td style="border-color: #000000;">Set lunch costs <strong data-start="898" data-end="912"> £ {30 | thirty}</strong> per personPortions probably of <strong data-start="948" data-end="961">{average}</strong> size</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>', NULL, 'summary_completion', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', '[{"content": "<p data-path-to-node=\"2\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"2\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">IELTS LISTENING SCRIPT: RESTAURANT ADVICE</strong></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"3\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">WOMAN:</strong> I’ve been meaning to ask you for some advice about restaurants – I need to book somewhere to celebrate my sister’s 30th birthday and I liked the sound of that place you went to for your mum’s 50th.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"4\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"4\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">MAN:</strong> The Junction? Yeah, I’d definitely recommend that for a special occasion. We had a great time there. Everyone really enjoyed it.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"5\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"5\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">WOMAN:</strong> Where is it again? I can’t remember.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"6\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"6\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">MAN:</strong> It’s on Greyson Street, only about a two minute walk from the station.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"7\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"7\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">WOMAN:</strong> Oh, that’s good. I’d prefer not to have to drive anywhere. But I don’t want to have to walk too far either.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"8\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"8\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">MAN:</strong> Yes, the location’s perfect but that’s not necessarily why I’d recommend it. The food’s amazing. If you like <span style=\"background-color: #f3db7b;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"8\" data-index-in-node=\"114\">fish</strong> </span>(Q1) it’s probably the best restaurant in town for that. It’s always really fresh and there are lots of interesting dishes to choose from. But all the food is good there.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"9\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">WOMAN:</strong> Is it really expensive?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"10\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"10\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">MAN:</strong> It’s certainly not cheap but for a special occasion I think it’s fine. It’s got a great atmosphere and before dinner you can go up on the <span style=\"background-color: #f3db7b;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"10\" data-index-in-node=\"143\">roof</strong> </span>(Q2) and have a drink – it’s really nice up there but you need to book. It’s very popular as the views are spectacular.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"11\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"11\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">WOMAN:</strong> Sounds good. So that’s definitely a possibility then. Is there anywhere else you can think of?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"12\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"12\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">MAN:</strong> If you want somewhere a bit less formal then you could try Paloma.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"13\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"13\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">WOMAN:</strong> Where’s that? I haven’t heard of it.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"14\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"14\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">MAN:</strong> No, it’s quite new. It’s only been open a few months but it’s got a great reputation already. It’s in a really beautiful old building on Bow Street.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"15\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"15\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">WOMAN:</strong> Oh, I think I know where you mean – right beside the cinema?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"16\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"16\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">MAN:</strong> Yes, that’s it. I’ve only been there a couple of times but I was really impressed. The chef used to work at Don Felipe’s, apparently. I was really sorry when that closed down.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"17\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"17\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">WOMAN:</strong> So is all the food they serve <span style=\"background-color: #f3db7b;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"17\" data-index-in-node=\"37\">Spanish</strong> </span>(Q3), then?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"18\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"18\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">MAN:</strong> Yeah. You can get lots of small dishes to share – which always works really well if you’re in a group.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"19\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"19\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">WOMAN:</strong> Mmm. Worth thinking about.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"20\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"20\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">MAN:</strong> Yeah. There’s a lively atmosphere and the waiters are really friendly. The only thing is that you need to pay a £50 deposit to book a table.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"21\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"21\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">WOMAN:</strong> A lot of restaurants are doing that these days. I should have a look at the menu to check there’s a good choice of <span style=\"background-color: #f3db7b;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"21\" data-index-in-node=\"122\">vegetarian</strong> </span>(Q4) dishes. A couple of my friends have stopped eating meat.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"22\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"22\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">MAN:</strong> Not sure. I’d say the selection of those would be quite limited.</p>\n<hr data-path-to-node=\"23\">\n<p data-path-to-node=\"24\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"24\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">MAN:</strong> I’ve just thought of another idea. Have you been to The <span style=\"background-color: #f3db7b;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"24\" data-index-in-node=\"61\">Audley</strong> </span>(Q5)?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"25\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"25\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">WOMAN:</strong> No, don’t think I’ve heard of it. How’s it spelt?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"26\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"26\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">MAN:</strong> A-U-D-L-E-Y. You must have heard of it – there’s been a lot about it in the press.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"27\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"27\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">WOMAN:</strong> I don’t tend to pay much attention to that kind of thing. So where is it exactly?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"28\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"28\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">MAN:</strong> It’s in that <span style=\"background-color: #f3db7b;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"28\" data-index-in-node=\"18\">hotel</strong> </span>(Q6) near Baxter Bridge – on the top floor.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"29\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"29\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">WOMAN:</strong> Oh, the views would be incredible from up there.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"30\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">MAN:</strong> Yeah. I’d love to go. I can’t think of the chef’s name but she was a judge on that TV cookery show recently. And she’s written a couple of cookery books.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"31\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"31\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">WOMAN:</strong> Oh, Angela Frayn.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"32\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"32\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">MAN:</strong> That’s the one. Anyway, it’s had excellent <span style=\"background-color: #f3db7b;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"32\" data-index-in-node=\"48\">reviews</strong> </span>(Q7) from all the newspapers.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"33\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"33\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">WOMAN:</strong> That would be a memorable place for a celebration.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"34\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">MAN:</strong> Definitely. Obviously it’s worth going there just for the view but the food is supposed to be really special.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"35\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"35\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">WOMAN:</strong> She only likes cooking with <span style=\"background-color: #f3db7b;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"35\" data-index-in-node=\"35\">local</strong> </span>(Q8) products, doesn’t she?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"36\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"36\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">MAN:</strong> Yes. Everything at the restaurant has to be sourced within a short distance and absolutely nothing flown in from abroad.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"37\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"37\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">WOMAN:</strong> I imagine it’s really expensive though.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"38\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"38\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">MAN:</strong> Well, you could go for the set lunch. That’s quite reasonable for a top class restaurant: <span style=\"background-color: #f3db7b;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"38\" data-index-in-node=\"95\">£30</strong></span> (Q9) a head. In the evening I think it’d be more like £50.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"39\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"39\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">WOMAN:</strong> At least that, I should think. But I’m sure everyone would enjoy it. It’s not the kind of place you leave feeling hungry though, is it? With tiny portions?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"40\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"40\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">MAN:</strong> No, the reviews I’ve read didn’t mention that. I imagine they’d be <span style=\"background-color: #f3db7b;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"40\" data-index-in-node=\"72\">average</strong> </span>(Q10).</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"41\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"41\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">WOMAN:</strong> Well, that’s all great, thanks…</p>"}]', 0);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('05e338b0-ed1b-49d1-8c16-61f146a85560', '0d6f900e-11c0-401a-84e2-dc0ce5633373', 'matrix', 'Questions 1-6', '', '<p>The Passage has 8 paragraphs<strong> A-H</strong>.</p>
<p>Which paragraph contains the following information?</p>
<p>Choose the appropriate letter, A-H, in boxes 1-6 on your answer sheet.</p>', 'choose_a_title', 'null', 'null', 'null', '{"layoutType": "simple", "matrixItems": [{"itemText": "categorizations of fish by swimming speed", "correctCategoryLetter": "G"}, {"itemText": "an example of fish capable of maintaining fast swimming for a long time", "correctCategoryLetter": "H"}, {"itemText": "how fish control stability", "correctCategoryLetter": "E"}, {"itemText": "frequency of the muscle movement of fish", "correctCategoryLetter": "C"}, {"itemText": "a mechanical model of fish skeleton", "correctCategoryLetter": "B"}, {"itemText": "energy storage devices in a fish", "correctCategoryLetter": "D"}], "matrixCategories": [{"categoryText": "A", "categoryLetter": "A"}, {"categoryText": "B", "categoryLetter": "B"}, {"categoryText": "C", "categoryLetter": "C"}, {"categoryText": "D", "categoryLetter": "D"}, {"categoryText": "E", "categoryLetter": "E"}, {"categoryText": "F", "categoryLetter": "F"}, {"categoryText": "G", "categoryLetter": "G"}, {"categoryText": "H", "categoryLetter": "H"}]}', '[{"content": "<p data-path-to-node=\"4\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"4\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">1. G — {categorizations of fish by swimming speed}</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"5\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"5,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"5,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng:</strong> <em data-path-to-node=\"5,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"11\">“From these studies, <strong data-path-to-node=\"5,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"32\">we can broadly categorise fish into four groups: “sneakers”</strong>...; <strong data-path-to-node=\"5,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"96\">“stayers”</strong>...; <strong data-path-to-node=\"5,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"110\">“sprinters”</strong>...; and <strong data-path-to-node=\"5,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"130\">“crawlers”</strong>...”</em></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"5,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"5,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> \"Categorizations\" (các cách phân loại/nhóm) trùng khớp hoàn toàn với cụm \"broadly categorise fish into four groups\". Đoạn G liệt kê chi tiết 4 nhóm cá dựa trên đặc điểm tốc độ bơi và sức bền của chúng (gồm sneakers, stayers, sprinters, crawlers).</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"6\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"6\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">2. H — {an example of fish capable of maintaining fast swimming for a long time}</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"7\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"7,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"7,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng:</strong> <em data-path-to-node=\"7,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"11\">“...and anglers have recorded <strong data-path-to-node=\"7,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"41\">speeds in excess of 40 mph over longer periods for several species of tuna</strong>.”</em></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"7,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"7,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> \"Maintaining fast swimming for a long time\" (duy trì bơi nhanh trong một thời gian dài) tương ứng với cụm từ \"speeds in excess of 40 mph over longer periods\" (tốc độ vượt quá 40 dặm/giờ trong các khoảng thời gian dài hơn). Ví dụ cụ thể (<em data-path-to-node=\"7,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"249\">an example</em>) được đưa ra ở đây chính là loài cá ngừ (<strong data-path-to-node=\"7,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"301\">tuna</strong>).</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"8\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"8\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">3. E — {how fish control stability}</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"9\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"9,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng:</strong> <em data-path-to-node=\"9,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"11\">“But it must be emphasized that the swimming movements are produced by the whole of the muscular body... <strong data-path-to-node=\"9,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"116\">Their main function [of the fins] is to control the stability and direction of the fish</strong>...”</em></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"9,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> \"Control stability\" (kiểm soát độ ổn định/thăng bằng). Đoạn E giải thích cơ chế này phụ thuộc vào bộ phận nào trên cơ thể cá, đó chính là chức năng cốt lõi của các vây (<em data-path-to-node=\"9,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"181\">fins</em>): khi nước đi qua cơ thể, cá dùng vây để tạo lực đẩy về hướng nó muốn đi nhằm giữ thăng bằng và định hướng.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"10\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"10\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">4. C — {frequency of the muscle movement of fish}</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"11\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"11,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"11,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng:</strong> <em data-path-to-node=\"11,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"11\">“The muscles on each side of the spine contract... causing a wave-like movement to pass down the body... <strong data-path-to-node=\"11,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"116\">The frequency of the waves varies from about 50/min in the dogfish to 170/min in the mackerel</strong>.”</em></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"11,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"11,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> \"Muscle movement\" (chuyển động của cơ) trong đoạn C được mô tả là sự co bóp tạo thành chuyển động dạng sóng (<em data-path-to-node=\"11,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"121\">wave-like movement</em>). Đoạn này cung cấp thông tin cụ thể về tần suất (<strong data-path-to-node=\"11,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"190\">frequency</strong>) của các sóng cơ này biến thiên từ 50 lần/phút ở cá nhám góc cho đến 170 lần/phút ở cá thu.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"12\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"12\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">5. B — {a mechanical model of fish skeleton}</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"13\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"13,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"13,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng:</strong> <em data-path-to-node=\"13,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"11\">“Fish rely on their <strong data-path-to-node=\"13,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"31\">skeleton</strong>, fins, and muscles to move. The primary function of the skeleton is to aid movement of other parts. <strong data-path-to-node=\"13,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"140\">Their skull acts as a fulcrum and their vertebrae act as levers</strong>.”</em></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"13,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"13,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> \"A mechanical model\" (một mô hình cơ học) được tác giả xây dựng bằng cách ví các bộ phận trong hệ xương của cá (<strong data-path-to-node=\"13,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"124\">skeleton</strong>) giống như các cấu kiện cơ khí công nghiệp: hộp sọ đóng vai trò như một điểm tựa (<strong data-path-to-node=\"13,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"215\">fulcrum</strong>) và các đốt sống đóng vai trò như những chiếc đòn bẩy (<strong data-path-to-node=\"13,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"278\">levers</strong>).</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"14\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"14\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">6. D — {energy storage devices in a fish}</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"15\">\n<li>\n<p id=\"p-rc_bfecbb9c4946d150-37\" data-path-to-node=\"15,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"15,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng:</strong> <em data-path-to-node=\"15,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"11\">“...the much smaller areas at the roots of the fins and in a strip along the centre of each flan<span class=\"citation-518 citation-519\">k comprise </span><strong data-path-to-node=\"15,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"118\"><span class=\"citation-518 citation-519\">red muscle. The red muscle receives a good supply of blood and contains ampler quantities of fat and glycogen, the storage form of glucose, which is used for most day-to-day swimming movements</span></strong><span class=\"citation-518 citation-519\">.”</span></em><span class=\"citation-518 citation-519 citation-end-519\"><sup class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"1\"><!----></sup></span><span class=\"citation-518 citation-end-518\"><sup class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"2\"><!----></sup></span></p>\n<!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></li>\n<li>\n<p id=\"p-rc_bfecbb9c4946d150-38\" data-path-to-node=\"15,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"15,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\"><span class=\"citation-516 citation-517\">Giải thích:</span></strong><span class=\"citation-516 citation-517 citation-end-517\"> \"Energy stora<sup class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"3\"><!----></sup></span><span class=\"citation-516 citation-end-516\">ge devices\" (các phân tử/thiết bị lưu trữ năng l<sup class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"4\"><!----></sup></span>ượng) được định danh cụ thể trong đoạn D là các mô cơ đỏ (<em data-path-to-node=\"15,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"131\">red muscle</em>), nơi tích trữ một lượng lớn chất béo (<em data-path-to-node=\"15,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"181\">fat</em>) và glycogen - dạng tích trữ của đường glucose (<em data-path-to-node=\"15,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"233\">the storage form of glucose</em>) để cung cấp năng lượng cho cá bơi lội hàng ngày.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>"}]', 0);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('8af1e822-ac48-4565-b8dc-2aa3186fb0bf', 'a2a298b7-d8c1-4d89-bbcd-872dc7bb5b9c', 'radio', 'Questions 27 - 30', '', '<p>Choose the correct answers</p>', 'multiple_choice', '[{"correct": 1, "options": [{"option_text": "A. It affects family relationships."}, {"option_text": "B. It leads to health problems later in life."}, {"option_text": "C. It makes childhood less enjoyable."}], "question": "Ravi thinks parents should be more concerned about the decline of outdoor play because"}, {"correct": 0, "options": [{"option_text": "A. Revise their aims."}, {"option_text": "B. Spend more money on it."}, {"option_text": "C. Listen to the views of parents."}], "question": "What does Ravi say that schools should do with regard to outdoor play?"}, {"correct": 0, "options": [{"option_text": "A. They tend not to be allowed on farmland."}, {"option_text": "B. They receive more supervision outdoors."}, {"option_text": "C. They spend more time outdoors than city children."}], "question": "What did Smith and Barker say about children in rural areas?"}, {"correct": 2, "options": [{"option_text": "A. Its findings are inconclusive."}, {"option_text": "B. It is too old to be useful."}, {"option_text": "C. Its focus is limited. "}], "question": " What problem does Dr Chang highlight about Smith and Barker’s research?"}]', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', 3);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('a18b18cb-b549-493a-a1a5-c99764dcc76e', '0fe88398-e380-44ce-9420-98b7d4b9252f', 'radio', 'Questions 33–37', NULL, '<p>Choose the correct answer.</p>
', 'multiple_choice_single', '[{"correct": 1, "options": [{"content": "focusing more on MONA as the leading attraction."}, {"content": "combining trips to MONA with visits to other galleries."}, {"content": "encouraging visitors to do activities that are not connected with art galleries."}, {"content": "improving the quality of promotional information about Tasmania’s galleries."}], "question": "Luke Martin plans to promote tourism in Tasmania by"}, {"correct": 0, "options": [{"content": "the man who founded the gallery"}, {"content": "its location close to a river"}, {"content": "visitors’ responses to the gallery spaces"}, {"content": "the striking architecture of the building"}], "question": "According to the writer, what is especially interesting about MONA?"}, {"correct": 3, "options": [{"content": "There is a great number of exhibits."}, {"content": "Visitors tend to come in family groups."}, {"content": "Many of the works are difficult to understand."}, {"content": "The gallery has a physical effect on visitors."}], "question": "Why do visitors spend a long time at the gallery?"}, {"correct": 1, "options": [{"content": "Older people spend longer there than younger people do."}, {"content": "A wide variety of people are interested in MONA."}, {"content": "The majority of visitors are young people."}, {"content": "The visitors are representative of gallery enthusiasts generally."}], "question": "What does the writer say about the visitors to MONA?"}, {"correct": 3, "options": [{"content": "to illustrate how interesting they are to visitors of modern galleries"}, {"content": "to explain why they are displayed in a separate section of the gallery"}, {"content": "to argue that Walsh''s collection is among the best in the world"}, {"content": "to express admiration for the way that the exhibits are presented"}], "question": "Why does the writer mention the coins at MONA?"}]', 'null', 'null', 'null', '[{"content": "<p><strong data-path-to-node=\"2\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">33. Luke Martin plans to promote tourism in Tasmania by</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"3\">\n<li><strong data-path-to-node=\"3,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Đáp án: B (combining trips to MONA with visits to other galleries.)</strong></li>\n<li><strong data-path-to-node=\"3,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng:</strong> Đoạn <strong data-path-to-node=\"3,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"16\">D</strong>, dòng 1-2: &#8220;According to Martin, possibilities for <strong data-path-to-node=\"3,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"69\">packaging up MONA with visits to other galleries</strong> around Tasmania are being investigated.&#8221;</li>\n<li><strong data-path-to-node=\"3,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Cụm từ &#8220;packaging up&#8221; đồng nghĩa với &#8220;combining trips&#8221; (kết hợp các chuyến đi). Luke Martin đang nghiên cứu việc tạo ra các gói du lịch kết hợp MONA với các phòng triển lãm khác tại Tasmania.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong data-path-to-node=\"4\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">34. According to the writer, what is especially interesting about MONA?</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"5\">\n<li><strong data-path-to-node=\"5,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Đáp án: A (the man who founded the gallery)</strong></li>\n<li><strong data-path-to-node=\"5,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng:</strong> Đoạn <strong data-path-to-node=\"5,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"16\">E</strong>, dòng 2-4: &#8220;MONA’s ‘wow factor’ comes from the <strong data-path-to-node=\"5,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"65\">notoriety of David Walsh, the museum’s millionaire founder</strong>, and his choice of unusual artworks.&#8221;</li>\n<li><strong data-path-to-node=\"5,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Tác giả khẳng định yếu tố gây kinh ngạc (&#8220;wow factor&#8221;) của bảo tàng đến từ sự nổi tiếng (và tai tiếng) của người sáng lập David Walsh cùng những lựa chọn tác phẩm khác lạ của ông.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong data-path-to-node=\"6\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">35. Why do visitors spend a long time at the gallery?</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"7\">\n<li><strong data-path-to-node=\"7,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Đáp án: D (The gallery has a physical effect on visitors.)</strong></li>\n<li><strong data-path-to-node=\"7,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng:</strong> Đoạn <strong data-path-to-node=\"7,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"16\">F</strong>, dòng 8-10: &#8220;the urge to linger is a common feeling here. This is because the <strong data-path-to-node=\"7,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"96\">gallery engages all of the senses</strong>, and visitors often pause to experience the effect each artwork has on them.&#8221;</li>\n<li><strong data-path-to-node=\"7,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Việc bảo tàng tác động đến mọi giác quan (engages all of the senses) chính là một tác động vật lý/trực giác khiến khách tham quan muốn nán lại lâu hơn để cảm nhận tầm ảnh hưởng của mỗi tác phẩm.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong data-path-to-node=\"8\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">36. What does the writer say about the visitors to MONA?</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"9\">\n<li><strong data-path-to-node=\"9,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Đáp án: B (A wide variety of people are interested in MONA.)</strong></li>\n<li><strong data-path-to-node=\"9,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng:</strong> Đoạn <strong data-path-to-node=\"9,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"16\">F</strong>, dòng 11-14: &#8220;&#8230;definitely <strong data-path-to-node=\"9,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"46\">not just the normal gallery-goers</strong>. People from <strong data-path-to-node=\"9,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"93\">all kinds of socioeconomic backgrounds</strong> are curious about what lies within&#8230;&#8221;</li>\n<li><strong data-path-to-node=\"9,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Tác giả nhấn mạnh khách đến MONA không chỉ là những người hay đi xem triển lãm thông thường mà bao gồm mọi tầng lớp xã hội khác nhau, điều này tương ứng với &#8220;a wide variety of people&#8221;.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong data-path-to-node=\"10\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">37. Why does the writer mention the coins at MONA?</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"11\">\n<li><strong data-path-to-node=\"11,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Đáp án: D (to express admiration for the way that the exhibits are presented)</strong></li>\n<li><strong data-path-to-node=\"11,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng:</strong> Đoạn <strong data-path-to-node=\"11,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"16\">G</strong>, dòng 4-5: &#8220;For me, one of the <strong data-path-to-node=\"11,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"49\">intriguing outcomes</strong> of this strategy was an intensified feeling that the makers of the coins&#8230; were the great contemporary artists of their time.&#8221;</li>\n<li><strong data-path-to-node=\"11,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Việc đặt tiền cổ xen kẽ với nghệ thuật hiện đại là một chiến lược trưng bày mà tác giả thấy rất thú vị (intriguing). Cách trình bày này khiến cô ngưỡng mộ vì nó làm tôn vinh giá trị của những món đồ cổ như những tác phẩm nghệ thuật đương đại thực thụ.</li>\n</ul>\n"}]', 1);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('89db683d-cfcb-468b-ab8e-80a4a8b71687', '0d78bc92-e925-46c5-9ef8-0664e6cfbc3d', 'matrix', 'Quetsions 22-26', '', '<p>Match each statement with the correct person, A, B, C or D.</p>
<p><em><strong>NB</strong> </em>You may use any letter more than once.</p>', 'choose_a_title', 'null', 'null', 'null', '{"layoutType": "standard", "legendTitle": "List of people", "matrixItems": [{"itemText": "There ought to be restrictions on where you can buy some herbal medicines.", "correctCategoryLetter": "A"}, {"itemText": "The authorities stopped supporting one project without a good reason.", "correctCategoryLetter": "B"}, {"itemText": "The herbal medicine industry has an effect on the environment where some plant-based medicines are found.", "correctCategoryLetter": "D"}, {"itemText": "New Zealand has the human resources and natural environment to grow herbs commercially.", "correctCategoryLetter": "A"}, {"itemText": " It is essential for herbal medicines to have international certification, despite the cost.", "correctCategoryLetter": "C"}], "matrixCategories": [{"categoryText": "Phil Rasmussen", "categoryLetter": "A"}, {"categoryText": "Malcolm Douglas", "categoryLetter": "B"}, {"categoryText": "Sandra Clair", "categoryLetter": "C"}, {"categoryText": "Isla Burgess", "categoryLetter": "D"}]}', '[{"content": "<p data-path-to-node=\"24\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"24\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">22. There ought to be restrictions on where you can buy some herbal medicines. — {A} Phil Rasmussen</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"25\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"25,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"25,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng (Đoạn F):</strong> <em data-path-to-node=\"25,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"20\">“According to <strong data-path-to-node=\"25,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"34\">Rasmussen</strong>, some herbs should <strong data-path-to-node=\"25,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"63\">require a prescription</strong>… consumers <strong data-path-to-node=\"25,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"99\">shouldn’t be able to go to their local supermarket and buy St John’s Wort</strong>…”</em></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"25,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"25,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Rasmussen cho rằng một số loại thảo dược cần được kê đơn và không nên được bán tự do ở siêu thị (đây chính là sự hạn chế về nơi mua).</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"26\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"26\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">23. The authorities stopped supporting one project without a good reason. — {B} Malcolm Douglas</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"27\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"27,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"27,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng (Đoạn A):</strong> <em data-path-to-node=\"27,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"20\">“It was an <strong data-path-to-node=\"27,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"31\">unjustified move, according to agronomist Malcolm Douglas</strong>, based on a number of inaccurate views…”</em></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"27,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"27,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Douglas cho rằng việc chính phủ ngừng cấp vốn cho nghiên cứu cây arnica là một hành động “không chính đáng” (unjustified/without a good reason).</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"28\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"28\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">24. The herbal medicine industry has an effect on the environment where some plant-based medicines are found. — {D} Isla Burgess</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"29\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"29,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"29,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng (Đoạn F):</strong> <em data-path-to-node=\"29,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"20\">“<strong data-path-to-node=\"29,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"21\">Isla Burgess</strong>… ‘The great majority of these are harvested from the wild, so they each have an <strong data-path-to-node=\"29,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"116\">impact on their local ecosystem</strong>.’”</em></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"29,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"29,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Burgess nhấn mạnh việc thu hoạch thảo dược hoang dã gây tác động đến hệ sinh thái địa phương (môi trường).</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"30\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">25. New Zealand has the human resources and natural environment to grow herbs commercially. — {A} Phil Rasmussen</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"31\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"31,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"31,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng (Đoạn A):</strong> <em data-path-to-node=\"31,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"20\">“…huge potential for New Zealand to develop a herb industry based on the <strong data-path-to-node=\"31,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"95\">excellent growing conditions and expertise</strong> there, according to <strong data-path-to-node=\"31,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"158\">Phil Rasmussen</strong>…”</em></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"31,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"31,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> “Growing conditions” tương ứng với môi trường tự nhiên, “expertise” (chuyên môn) tương ứng với nguồn lực con người.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"32\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"32\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">26. It is essential for herbal medicines to have international certification, despite the cost. — {C} Sandra Clair</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"33\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"33,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"33,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng (Đoạn E):</strong> <em data-path-to-node=\"33,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"20\">“So too is the range produced by <strong data-path-to-node=\"33,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"53\">Sandra Clair</strong>, who says that such <strong data-path-to-node=\"33,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"86\">assurance is expensive but necessary</strong> if you want to export herbal remedies…”</em></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"33,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"33,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Sandra Clair khẳng định việc đảm bảo tiêu chuẩn (international certification/assurance) là tốn kém nhưng cần thiết (essential).</p>\n</li>\n</ul>"}]', 2);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('27340b72-fe6f-4ebb-8b4b-a35f7825d56c', '8980edf4-2b69-4169-aade-705346dd1e9a', 'radio', 'Questions 11–16', '', '<p>Choose the correct answer.</p>', 'multiple_choice', '[{"correct": 0, "options": [{"option_text": "seen as an opportunity to learn."}, {"option_text": "predicted and minimised."}, {"option_text": "avoided at all costs"}], "question": "Arthur feels that when starting a business, mistakes should be"}, {"correct": 0, "options": [{"option_text": "sometimes reduce people''s chances of success."}, {"option_text": "be increased by reading self-help books."}, {"option_text": "ensure good results on business courses."}], "question": "Recent American studies found that confidence will"}, {"correct": 2, "options": [{"option_text": "listen to their colleagues'' advice."}, {"option_text": "get professional help when things go wrong."}, {"option_text": "remain concentrated on their aims."}], "question": "The American studies recommended that new entrepreneurs"}, {"correct": 1, "options": [{"option_text": "He relied on what he already knew."}, {"option_text": "He hired an expert to take care of it."}, {"option_text": "He realised its importance too late."}], "question": "What does Arthur say about his own experience of marketing?"}, {"correct": 2, "options": [{"option_text": "They are ambitious for their company."}, {"option_text": "They can deal with difficult people."}, {"option_text": "They earn the respect of their workforce."}], "question": "What does Arthur think Is an important quality shared by good leaders?"}, {"correct": 0, "options": [{"option_text": "He advises being cautious"}, {"option_text": "He favours a long-term view."}, {"option_text": "He believes it is financially advantageous."}], "question": "What does Arthur say about taking risks?"}]', 'null', 'null', 'null', '[{"content": "<p data-path-to-node=\"3\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Presenter:</strong> Everybody dreams of becoming a millionaire one day, so we asked Arthur Knowles, who made his millions in the plumbing business, to give the budding entrepreneurs among you a few tips on how to make your first million. Arthur, welcome to the programme.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"4\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"4\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Arthur:</strong> Thanks, Sue.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"5\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"5\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Presenter:</strong> So Arthur, what advice do you have for our listeners?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"6\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"6\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Arthur:</strong> Well, one thing I’ve heard people say is that when you’re starting up a business, you can’t afford to make mistakes. Well, I believe in the old saying: a person who never made a mistake never made anything.<span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"> <strong data-path-to-node=\"6\" data-index-in-node=\"215\">(Q11) You can’t really predict when you’ll make mistakes, and you have to look at them as a positive experience — and one that means you won’t make the same mistake again.</strong></span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"7\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"7\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Arthur:</strong> You need to be able to cope with the world of business, but according to recent American business school studies, believing in yourself isn’t enough by itself to guarantee success. <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"7\" data-index-in-node=\"189\">(Q12) Confidence can be a good thing, but a person can have too much confidence, and people who try to learn to be confident by buying those how-to-succeed books are just wasting their time.</strong></span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"8\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"8\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Arthur:</strong> The advice given in these American studies was that being a successful entrepreneur comes down to having the right attitude. It’s no good getting depressed every time something goes wrong. <strong data-path-to-node=\"8\" data-index-in-node=\"197\"><span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\">(Q13) Always keep your goals in mind and never give up</span>.</strong> And don’t listen to all the people around you who say, “Oh, this will never work.”</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"9\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Arthur:</strong> One thing I’ve learned in business is that you don’t have to be an expert in everything, like marketing for example. When I started my business, I tried to do it all myself, but I soon realised that although I knew everything there was to know about plumbing, I didn’t have much idea about how to sell my ideas. <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9\" data-index-in-node=\"320\">(Q14) So I got someone who knew more about this to take care of the marketing side of things for me.</strong></span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"10\"><span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"10\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Arthur:</strong> <strong data-path-to-node=\"10\" data-index-in-node=\"8\">(Q15) And as for leadership, well, you’ve got to be someone your workers look up to because you’ve been seen to make the right decisions.</strong></span> You have to be able to control people, but listen to them at the same time. Some people are driven to make their companies successful, but that too often leads to a ruthless approach.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"11\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"11\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Arthur:</strong> Then there’s the question of taking risks, even calculated ones. <strong data-path-to-node=\"11\" data-index-in-node=\"73\"><span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\">(Q16) I personally feel it’s actually better to tread carefully when it comes to taking short-term risks</span>.</strong> You need a degree of vision, certainly, but it’s easy to get carried away by your desire to increase profits, and if things go wrong, you can end up losing more than you gain.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"14\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"14\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Arthur:</strong> So if you have a great idea for a business, what should you do next? Well, the first thing to ask yourself is whether there’s a need for your product or service. <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"14\" data-index-in-node=\"170\">(Q17-18) Can you cater for people’s needs better than existing companies?</strong></span> You don’t need to worry about whether it’s original or not, because there isn’t always enough demand for completely new ideas.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"15\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"15\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Arthur:</strong> <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"15\" data-index-in-node=\"8\">(Q17-18) And the second thing to ask yourself is not what colour should the packet be or how much should it cost, but do I care enough about this idea to dedicate the next 10 years of my life to it?</strong></span> Because realistically, that’s how long it will take.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"16\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"16\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Presenter:</strong> Tell us how you got started, Arthur. How do you explain your early success?</p>\n<p id=\"p-rc_a2ca37fe4d43f8dc-54\" data-path-to-node=\"17\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"17\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Arthur:</strong> <span class=\"citation-221 citation-end-221\">Well, I started my business just as the economy was going into a recession, which wasn’t the best time, and I was lucky to survive, especially as the banks weren’t being particularly supportive to small businesses at that tim</span>e.</p>\n<div class=\"source-inline-chip-container ng-star-inserted\"> </div>\n<p data-start=\"162\" data-end=\"430\"> </p>\n<p id=\"p-rc_a2ca37fe4d43f8dc-55\" data-path-to-node=\"18\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"18\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Arthur:</strong> If I’d listened to the business advice I was given back then, I’d never have got started. <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"18\" data-index-in-node=\"98\">(Q19-20) <span class=\"citation-220 citation-end-220\">My strengths were that I knew I could provide a better service than my competitors, who really hadn’t spotted the opportunities that were out there, and that my wife had a good job and was able to pay the household bills while I was getting the company on its fee</span>t.</strong></span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"19\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"19\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Arthur:</strong> The first couple of years were very tough, but I knew I would make it eventually.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"20\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"20\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Presenter:</strong> OK, now we’re going to take some calls from listeners.</p>"}]', 0);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('30bc9d12-9b83-4189-9b2b-f32627ed1b70', '907b7ffc-b096-49c4-a1c9-3301e8020730', 'fillup', 'Questions 9–10', '<div class="quests-inner-desc">
